Ugh... I'm so hungry...
I wonder if Producer brought back anything to eat~
Oh, Kogane-chan.

Fuyuko~!
Did you also come here because you were hungry~?

Yeah! Hehe, maybe it's because of the training camp?
I'm feeling hungrier than usual...

I get ya~. But hey, bein' famished is proof
you've been workin' hard in lessons, right?
What will Fuyuko eat?

Fuyu brought some pudding,
so maybe have that.

In that case, I'll whip somethin' up! Why don't we eat together,
Fuyuko, and head back to the room in high spirits?

Huh?
K-Kogane-chan...?

Hehe, sounds good, sounds good.
I've got plenty of vegetables, meat, and noodles...!

With all that,
I can make a big batch of my special champon!

I-It's alright, Kogane-chan!
Fuyu have the pudding...

Puddin' is nice, but havin' a warm belly with a 
veggie-packed hot pot helps you sleep better~

Tomorrow, we'll be movin' around like today~
Eatin' lots and buildin' stamina is definitely the way to go...!

Heheh, thanks.
Well then, fuyu will just have a little bit.
